divs: sighting detailsi was out walking alone, made it mid block of henry place, between garretson \ cromwell. lights caught my eye. looked up observed slowly moving lights, red\orange\yellow. the light appeared to be to be attached but i could see stars between them. seemed to be headed to the ocean in a brooklyn direction i honestly belive the lights were a one of those military predator unmanned aircraft or the stealth helicopter they took out binladin with the light slowed and speed up together. the lights were forward direction facing like a flashlight once the light went out of my field of view it was as if it vanished, but i could still see the second light until it to moved away from me. i dont know what it was reporting it cause other folks have seen them aswell sorry no photo or video
